{"tid":874051,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"關於Whatsapp Backup","createTime":"2018-10-24T01:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T02:51:39.000Z","uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"453693cd7973b3901d163dfe9fea5dd2c8e4687f","tid":874051,"uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T01:53:18.000Z","msg":"話說我whatsapp有個對話嘅Media全部無過落以家用緊部電話到，淨係得文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我新機已經開始用緊，唔知點樣先可以將啲媒體過埋去新機到，又唔會搞到無左啲對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過Apple啲人話無得merge埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是send左email俾whatsapp又答答下又無答我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/094516_d790733487a69cd13c0b8c04f5f6c19d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F094516_d790733487a69cd13c0b8c04f5f6c19d.png&h=f1cd67d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係以家部電話嘅whatsapp，我舊機個啲仲係到㗎，但唔知點樣link返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/094818_e1e28ee19de68a29ccd4d9f6d36f1525.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F094818_e1e28ee19de68a29ccd4d9f6d36f1525.png&h=856baffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係whatsapp嘅回覆，我唔係好明。如果我restore左舊機嘅backup，咁我以家用個部電話開始嘅對話會唔會無左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望有好心人可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞左好耐都唔知點好，時不時攞返舊電話出黎睇，又驚一日壞機以後都無得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86fcb948eae911cda8a0c6a62f50d3cc011f374","tid":874051,"uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e5aee7b16732ae78fc1ccad99f596f22420fa9","tid":874051,"uid":8659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"應該冇計<br />\n你趁舊機仲work DL哂D野落黎先啦<br />\n<br />\nBTW呢度遊戲台"},{"pid":"b5fd405107b2ad07784b96ce4b112900bb9cb180","tid":874051,"uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e5aee7b16732ae78fc1ccad99f596f22420fa9","tid":874051,"uid":8659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"應該冇計<br />\n你趁舊機仲work DL哂D野落黎先啦<br />\n<br />\nBTW呢度遊戲台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"係喎點解開左係遊戲台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢email覆我個個alternative我又唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005ac5b011b971c9ceb0bb386caa81d097299643","tid":874051,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"iphone轉iPhone 定android轉iPhone"},{"pid":"101063e67209b33c0ac963d24d8832e155937d5d","tid":874051,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5fd405107b2ad07784b96ce4b112900bb9cb180","tid":874051,"uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e5aee7b16732ae78fc1ccad99f596f22420fa9","tid":874051,"uid":8659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:06:43.000Z","msg":"應該冇計<br />\n你趁舊機仲work DL哂D野落黎先啦<br />\n<br />\nBTW呢度遊戲台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"係喎點解開左係遊戲台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢email覆我個個alternative我又唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"你咁做新機既新對話會冇哂"},{"pid":"5788c9c5586e718bb758234c05cc16b548b29674","tid":874051,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"101063e67209b33c0ac963d24d8832e155937d5d","tid":874051,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p